</taxonomicName>
Usinger; Piti, May 15, Usinger; Merizo, June 11, on corn, Swezey; Piti, June 15, Swezey; Fonte Valley, Aug. 
<emphasis id="8DB6EAE1FFAA1B1DFC1EF87B04E641CF" bold="true" box="[964,992,1998,2041]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="170">7,</emphasis>
